\sum _{p\leq n}\frac{1}{p}=C+\ln  \ln  n+O\left(\frac{1}{\ln  n}\right)~~~(1)
C\overset{\text{def}}{=}1-\ln\ln 2+\displaystyle\int_2^\infty \left(-\ln t + \sum_{p \leqslant t}\frac{\ln p}{p}\right)\frac{dt}{t (\ln t)^2}.
